answers.body_markdown:
You can use case and subquery 

hope this help :)

    UPDATE table_name SET id= ( case when product_name= &#39;apple&#39; then &#39;p1&#39; when product_name= &#39;grape&#39; then &#39;p3&#39; else id END );

```sql
UPDATE table_name SET id= (
  case when product_name= &#39;apple&#39; then &#39;p1&#39; 
  when product_name= &#39;grape&#39; then &#39;p3&#39; 
  else id END );
```

